    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "He said the club was going to petition the President of the United",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "States to make public all government information on flying saucers.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "He also stated that by letter, September 25, 1954, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "advised him he was a group leader in the club, and his duties would",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "be to keep up with latest developments and advise his group, the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "names of which he would receive from Miss [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "The Detroit Free Press of September 29, 1954, said in an",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "article that the DFSC met September 28, 1954, and DESMOND LESLIE,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "British flying saucer authority, spoke, stating that GEORGE ADAMSKI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "made contact two years ago with space people in a California desert.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] advised he received a letter September 30,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "1954, from [REDACTED], setting out the discussion",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "group in the Farmington area as:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
