      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Mich",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Mich",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "He received a letter from her October 4, 1954, adding to the above",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "list:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED] on October 13, 1954, said that [REDACTED] asked him",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "to call a meeting October 18, 1954. At this time, he said he felt",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "he knew less about the club than anyone; but he thought it would make",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "a good cover for subversive activities.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "He advised the object of group discussions, according to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
